{"tid":267070,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司文化真係好重要","createTime":"2017-06-02T03:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T06:17:31.000Z","uid":61586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da8d8d4e6981658b71e16731fd841abda68afe97","tid":267070,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:40:18.000Z","msg":"以前揸輕鐵,明明係自己做自己野,日日自己揸車,都可以有好多小圈子<br />\n呢個講果個唔好,成班麻甩都好多是非<br />\n<br />\n又做過中小企,做多過講,老細成日鬧人又成日搗亂<br />\n一係就唔見左人,得閒返黎阻住哂做野<br />\n老細唔係度效率高幾倍,但都唔多溝通<br />\n而且成日要幫手隔離部門做野,因為所謂部門其實個個都係得一兩條友<br />\n咩都要做,趕唔切就成個OFFICE俾人屌<br />\n<br />\n而家走左去做公營機構,三日唔埋兩日開會<br />\n我呢啲小薯仔,入去就係坐會,全程透明唔講野<br />\n一個下午咁就無撚左<br />\n又少野做,睇落好似好多,其實一陣就做完<br />\n又無人會篤住你做<br />\n<br />\n但係學唔到隔黎部門啲野,感覺如果唔搏上位好快就會五年十年咁過左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純感慨"},{"pid":"8b4b6404a0ac2cc0bc6da9b1e0a9d833db75a698","tid":267070,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"公司得十幾人 冇小圈子<br />\n相處得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c61604a38a456062493b727e4415eb08d2f500","tid":267070,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公司得十幾人 冇小圈子<br />\n相處得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老細好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393d922f02474f5462e7d610faa556bc7e158c63","tid":267070,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公司得十幾人 冇小圈子<br />\n相處得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老細好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三個老細 得一個煩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e796e23898f18d56c3b5f108f7642d8c5ef20528","tid":267070,"uid":61586,"like":0,"d